WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.900
Koul Nussbaumer Knaflik - ma’lumotlarni hikoya 
qilib berish bo‘yicha mutaxassis.

00:00:05.900 --> 00:00:08.325
O‘zining "Ma’lumotlar bilan hikoya qilish" kitobida,

00:00:08.325 --> 00:00:12.375
u ma’lumotlar bilan aloqa qilish 
bo‘yicha oltita dars beradi.

00:00:12.375 --> 00:00:16.530
Birinchidan, vizualizatsiyangiz 
kontekstini tushunib oling.

00:00:16.530 --> 00:00:20.235
Ikkinchidan, tegishli vizual 
ko‘rinishni tanlang.

00:00:20.235 --> 00:00:24.640
Biz oxirgi darsda eng keng tarqalgan 
vizualizatsiya usullarini ko‘rgan edik.

00:00:24.640 --> 00:00:27.135
Uchinchidan, shovqinni yo‘q qiling.

00:00:27.135 --> 00:00:31.920
Tasvirdan Sizning fikringizni yetkazishga 
halaqit qiladigan qismlarni olib tashlang.

00:00:31.920 --> 00:00:35.775
To‘rtinchidan, diqqatni kerakli 
joyga qarating.

00:00:35.775 --> 00:00:41.920
Tomoshabinlar e’tiborga olishlari va ular amal qilishlari 
kerak bo‘lgan xususiyatlarni ajratib ko‘rsating.

00:00:41.920 --> 00:00:44.765
Beshinchidan, dizayner kabi o‘ylab ko‘ring.

00:00:44.765 --> 00:00:46.830
Bu men uchun eng qiyin jihat,

00:00:46.830 --> 00:00:50.450
ammo biz bularga ushbu darsimizda 
ko‘proq e’tibor qaratamiz.

00:00:50.450 --> 00:00:53.070
Va nihoyat, sizda hikoya hosil bo‘lsin.

00:00:53.070 --> 00:00:57.820
Siz namoyish qiladigan vizual vositalar tomoshabinni 
harakatga keltiradigan hikoyani taqdim etishingiz kerak.

00:00:57.820 --> 00:00:59.550
Oldingi darsda

00:00:59.550 --> 00:01:03.360
siz turli xil ma’lumot turlari bilan ishlatilishi mumkin bo‘lgan diagrammalar haqida bilib oldingiz.

00:01:03.360 --> 00:01:07.110
Ushbu darsda biz ushbu ma’lumotlaringizni eng 
yaxshi ko‘rinishda va xabaringizni eng 

00:01:07.110 --> 00:01:11.380
yaxshi etkazadigan qilib tasvirlashga yordam 
beradigan yakuniy qismlarga e’tibor qaratmoqchimiz.

